{
    "body": "<p>You breathe out a blast of energy. Creatures in the affected area take 1d6 points of energy damage per caster level (maximum of 12d6). A successful Reflex save results in half damage. The spell's effect and energy type depend on the type of dragon scale used:</p><p id=\"black-dragon:\"><i>Black dragon:</i> 60-foot line of acid.</p><p id=\"blue-or-bronze-dragon:\"><i>Blue or bronze dragon:</i> 60-foot line of electricity.</p><p id=\"green-dragon:\"><i>Green dragon:</i> 30-foot cone of acid.</p><p id=\"gold-or-red-dragon:\"><i>Gold or red dragon:</i> 30-foot cone of fire.</p><p id=\"silver-or-white-dragon:\"><i>Silver or white dragon:</i> 30-foot cone of cold.</p><p id=\"brass-dragon:\"><i>Brass dragon:</i> 60-foot line of fire.</p><p id=\"copper-dragon:\"><i>Copper dragon:</i> 60-foot line of acid.</p>", 
